404
00:21:02,540 --> 00:21:03,830
Qui c'est ?

405
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:05,170
Tu as lu Forbes ?

406
00:21:05,180 --> 00:21:07,260
Je n'étais pas très bien, en prison.

407
00:21:07,270 --> 00:21:09,330
<i>Ted Earley Ex-PDG, Attercliffe Capital
